# Copy to .env and fill in. All optional — Greenhouse + Lever + Workday need no keys.
# Workday login (email + password) goes in workday_answers.json, not here.

# Auto-clear Workday email verification: the filler asks for your Gmail App Password
# ONCE (hidden), then saves it encrypted via Windows DPAPI — you're not asked again.
# You do NOT need to set anything here. This env var is only an unattended override
# that skips the saved blob; if set, it sits in PLAINTEXT on this machine.
#   App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords  (needs 2-Step Verification)
#   Reset it later:  python -m jobagent.workday.inbox --forget
# GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
